videos.headline: Callaway Mosses defender for Tennessee TD
videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano lofts a pass to Marquez Callaway, who makes an athletic grab over a Kentucky defender for a 17-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Callaway Mosses defender for Tennessee TD) 2019/11/9 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vols WR Palmer tight ropes end zone for sick TD
videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano sends pass Josh Palmer's way, who makes the grab and drops a foot down to complete the 12-yard touchdown.
